希格斯在1964年於[[蘇格蘭高地|蘇格蘭高地]]健行時突然獲得靈感<ref>Collins, Nick (4 July 2012)  "Higgs boson: Prof Stephen Hawking loses $100 bet". ''The Telegraph.'' London.</ref><ref>"Scientists discover 'God' particle." (4 July 2012) ''The Herald.'' Glasgow.</ref>，隨後在[[美國物理學會|美國物理學會]]《[[物理快報|物理快報]]》<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0031916364911369|pages=132–133|title=Broken symmetries, massless particles and gauge fields|journal=Physics Letters|volume=12|issue=2|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1016/0031-9163(64)91136-9|author=P.W. Higgs|archive-date=2022-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220616045118/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0031916364911369}}</ref>發表論文解決南部-戈德斯通定理留下的難題。希格斯在論文中提出[[希格斯機制|希格斯機制]]理論，但是遭到《物理快報》退回<ref name=Guardian/>。於是他將論文轉投到《[[物理評論快報|物理評論快報]]》<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1103/physrevlett.13.508|title=Broken Symmetries and the Masses of Gauge Bosons|date=1964|journal=Physical Review Letters|volume=13|issue=16|pages=508–509|url=https://link.aps.org/doi/10.1103/PhysRevLett.13.508|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Peter W. Higgs}}{{Dead link}}</ref>，同時有另外五位科學家也獲得相同的結論，包括[[弗朗索瓦·恩格勒|弗朗索瓦·恩格勒]]、[[羅伯特·布繞特|羅伯特·布繞特]]<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1103/physrevlett.13.321|title=Broken Symmetry and the Mass of Gauge Vector Mesons|date=1964|journal=Physical Review Letters|volume=13|issue=9|pages=321–323|url=https://link.aps.org/doi/10.1103/PhysRevLett.13.321|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=F. Englert}}</ref>、[[傑拉德·古拉尼|傑拉德·古拉尼]]、[[卡爾·哈庚|卡爾·哈庚]]和[[湯姆·基博爾|湯姆·基博爾]]<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1103/physrevlett.13.585|title=Global Conservation Laws and Massless Particles|date=1964|journal=Physical Review Letters|volume=13|issue=20|pages=585–587|url=https://link.aps.org/doi/10.1103/PhysRevLett.13.585|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=G. S. Guralnik}}</ref>。這六位物理學者分別發表的三篇論文在《物理評論快報》50周年慶祝文獻中被公認為里程碑論文<ref>{{cite web |url=http://prl.aps.org/50years/milestones#1964 |title=Physical Review Letters - 50th Anniversary Milestone Papers |publisher=Prl.aps.org |date= |accessdate=2012-07-05 |archive-date=2010-01-10 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20100110134128/http://prl.aps.org/50years/milestones#1964 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

